Checklist before going live

1. Set "BYBIT_TESTNET=true" and "DRY_RUN=true", then run:
   
   cargo run --release
   
   Make sure the logs show something like:
   
   ""Found N base coins...""
   
   and that spread opportunities are being detected periodically.

2. Switch to:
   
   "BYBIT_TESTNET=true"
   "DRY_RUN=false"
   
   Verify that orders are actually being placed on the testnet (check them in the "testnet.bybit.com" interface) and confirm that "/gm" messages arrive in the selected Telegram chat.

3. Only after that should you switch to:
   
   "BYBIT_TESTNET=false"
   
   using your production API keys and a small "NOTIONAL_USDT" / "NOTIONAL_USDC" value for the first live run.
